      <h1>Meet Kuan Shin Bong</h1>
      <p>Bong grew up in a small village called Lawas in Sarawak, Malaysia. He has 11 other siblings and started from very humble beginnings. Bong is an avid traveller and foodie, always on the hunt for the most exciting and tasty foods. He makes Edwina’s favourite Malaysian dish, chilli crab. A trip to the chinese grocery store for fresh crab and ingredients is a must during his visits. She can sit at the dining table and pick at crab meat all day. Edwina’s passion for photography comes from her father as he is always documenting his food and travel through a camera lense (nowadays an iphone).</p>
