      <p>Yarko was born in Montreal, and grew up in Toronto and Mississauga. As a curious kid, he spent a lot of time exploring, making his own science projects, the best go-carts and winning races. He introduced Mike and Steve to a lot of cool things like camping, fishing, building Porsche motors, flying homemade remote control airplanes, vodka shots, and Led Zeppelin. Yarko is a really interesting character that inspires many, knows how to make us laugh, and knows how to make a Porsche really fly on race day.</p>
